:"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aw~alu AlEaziymapi","text_ar":"اَوَّلُ العَزِيمَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.) See Har, p. 345, and a verse cited voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tal~aAE","text_ar":"طَلَّاع"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b2-  Also the ↓ latter,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Strong determination"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"resolution."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ham~N","text_ar":"هَمٌّ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An object,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thing intended"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"meant"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"desired"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"determined upon, in the mind."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * TA.) See an ex. voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ham~N","text_ar":"حَمٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sam~N","text_ar":"سَمٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":": you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ham~uhu ka*aA","text_ar":"هَمُّهُ كَذَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His object is such a thing."},{"kind":"text","text":"―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ham~N","text_ar":"هَمٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Anxiety;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"disquietude,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"trouble, of mind; solicitude; care:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"grief,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sorrow:"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"distress,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"disquietude, affecting the heart"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mind, by reason of some harm,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"annoyance, that is expected to happen;"},{"kind":"text","text":"differing from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gam~N","text_ar":"غَمٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which signifies “ distress, or disquietude, affecting the heart or mind, by reason of what has happened: ” or both, as some say, signify the same [namely"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"distress,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"disquietude, of mind"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: the difference is asserted by 'Iyád and others. (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gm","text_ar":"غم"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ham~uhu baTonuhu","text_ar":"هَمُّهُ بَطْنُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His object of care,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of anxiety, is his belly"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bTn","text_ar":"بطن"},{"kind":"text","text":".) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA ham~a lahu A_il~aA baTonuhu","text_ar":"لَا هَمَّ لَهُ اـِلَّا بَطْنُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He has no object of care,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of anxiety, but his belly"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA in that art.) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ham~aka maA ham~aka","text_ar":"هَمَّكَ مَا هَمَّكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ham~aka maA EanaAka","text_ar":"هَمَّكَ مَا عَنَاكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ham~aka","text_ar":"هَمَّكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A*Abk","text_ar":"اذابك"},{"kind":"text","text":". (JK.) See also Freytag's Arab. Prov. ii. 880."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}